==English==
===Noun===

# '''Chuvash''' ({{IPAchar|Чӑваш чӗлхи}}) is an [[agglutinative]] language of the [[Bolgar]] branch of the [[Turkic]] language family and is spoken west of the [[Ural]] mountains in central [[Russia]]. Chuvash is the native language of the '''Chuvash''' people and an official language of [[Chuvashia]]. It is spoken by about two million people.

